    <scopecontent>
      <head>Scope and Content Note</head>
      <p>The Laura Riding Collection, 1923-1933, includes correspondence, poetry, and lists ofpotential subscribers to The Fugitive magazine. The collection is very minimal, containing 7 letters, 6 poems, and several pages oflists and notecards. The focus
        of this collection is Laura Riding&#8217;s connection to The Fugitive Magazine.</p>
    </scopecontent>
